Good app, although its usefulness depends on coverage; the more the merrier! The 'heat map' could be improved by better scaling - currently alternate bands cover 2x, then 5x, then 2x ... this has the effect of bunching both 1000 and 5000 cases per million into one colour, which is too broad IMO. It would be better if a scheme were chosen which gives more distinction where the numbers are greater, with less emphasis on showing differences between small numbers (a single case up or down has a massive effect where proportions are low).
